{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "workflowId": "run-build-skill",
  "skill": "run-build-skill",
  "description": "新規/更新 Capability 構築のフェーズ定義。各 phase は SKILL.md 本文の Step に対応し、kind_filter で適用対象 kind を限定する。kind_filter の語彙は二層: init-pre のみ Capability 7 kind (skill/agent/hook/command/plugin-composition/prompt/workflow)、init 以降は kind=skill のサブ種別 (run/ref/assign/delegate/wrap) を指す。",
  "phases": [
    {
      "id": "init-pre",
      "step": 0,
      "title": "kind 分岐ナビゲーション (Capability 7 kind → 適用フロー確定)",
      "kind_filter": ["skill", "agent", "hook", "command", "plugin-composition", "prompt", "workflow"],
      "resourceIds": ["schema-template-selection"],
      "output_artifact": "(kind / skeleton / kind別lint 選択の決定のみ。ファイル成果物なし)",
      "note": "全 Capability 7 kind の入口 (SKILL.md Step 0)。kind=skill の場合のみ init 以降のフェーズ (kind_filter = サブ種別 5 値) へ進む。非 skill kind は kind 語彙 (schemas/build-flags.schema.json#/properties/capability_kind) と対応表 (references/build-steps.md §I.1) で skeleton/出力先/lint を確定し、scaffold 相当の生成と Step 4 の kind 別 lint で完結する。"
    },
    {
      "id": "init",
      "step": 1,
      "title": "要求ヒアリングと L0/L1 解決",
      "dependsOn": ["init-pre"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "ref", "assign", "delegate", "wrap"],
      "resourceIds": ["ref-resource-map", "ref-build-steps", "schema-build-flags", "schema-build-plan"],
      "output_artifact": "eval-log/skill-brief.json + eval-log/build-plan.json",
      "note": "brief 確定直後に scripts/validate-build-plan.py --brief eval-log/skill-brief.json --out eval-log/build-plan.json で必須成果物集合 (flags/セクション/資産) を決定論導出する。以降の flag_required 付き phase の要否はこの plan.flags が正本 (モデル判断でフラグを省略しない)。充足は Step 4 の --check と p0-gate が機械検査する。"
    },
    {
      "id": "scaffold",
      "step": 2,
      "title": "kind→template 展開 / update 差分読込",
      "dependsOn": ["init"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "ref", "assign", "delegate", "wrap"],
      "resourceIds": ["schema-template-selection", "prompt-template-select", "prompt-scaffold"],
      "output_artifact": "plugins/<plugin>/skills/<skill>/SKILL.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "references",
      "step": 3,
      "title": "補助 references/ 生成",
      "dependsOn": ["scaffold"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "ref", "assign", "delegate", "wrap"],
      "resourceIds": ["ref-build-steps"],
      "output_artifact": "plugins/<plugin>/skills/<skill>/references/"
    },
    {
      "id": "scripts",
      "step": 4,
      "title": "決定論 scripts と lint 実行",
      "dependsOn": ["references"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "assign", "wrap", "delegate"],
      "resourceIds": ["schema-skill-build-trace"],
      "output_artifact": "eval-log/skill-build-trace.json",
      "verifier": "Step4 lint set including scripts/lint-feedback-contract.py --changed-only"
    },
    {
      "id": "templates",
      "step": 5,
      "title": "templates/_base + combinator 解決",
      "dependsOn": ["scaffold"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "ref", "assign", "delegate", "wrap"],
      "resourceIds": ["schema-template-selection"],
      "output_artifact": "templates/"
    },
    {
      "id": "assets",
      "step": 6,
      "title": "examples/ assets/ 生成",
      "dependsOn": ["references"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "ref", "assign", "wrap"],
      "resourceIds": [],
      "output_artifact": "examples/"
    },
    {
      "id": "prompts-emit",
      "step": 7,
      "title": "responsibility-slot ベースの prompt YAML 生成",
      "dependsOn": ["scaffold"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "assign", "delegate"],
      "flag_required": "--with-prompts",
      "flag_source": "eval-log/build-plan.json#/flags/with_prompts (brief.responsibilities から決定論導出)",
      "resourceIds": ["schema-responsibility-slot", "prompt-responsibility-emit"],
      "output_artifact": "prompts/<R-id>.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "evaluator-emit",
      "step": 8,
      "title": "pair evaluator 同時生成",
      "dependsOn": ["scaffold"],
      "kind_filter": ["assign"],
      "flag_required": "--with-evaluator",
      "flag_source": "eval-log/build-plan.json#/flags/with_evaluator (brief.generate_pair_evaluator から決定論導出)",
      "resourceIds": ["schema-build-flags"],
      "output_artifact": "plugins/<plugin>/skills/<pair>/"
    },
    {
      "id": "trace-write",
      "step": 9,
      "title": "skill-build-trace.json 章別記入と検証",
      "dependsOn": ["scripts"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "ref", "assign", "delegate", "wrap"],
      "resourceIds": ["schema-skill-build-trace", "prompt-trace-write"],
      "output_artifact": "eval-log/skill-build-trace.json",
      "note": "prompts-emit / evaluator-emit は flag_required の任意 phase。trace-write は必須 phase のため optional phase へ依存しない。任意成果物が存在する場合のみ trace に取り込む。loop実行系の feedback_contract は生成 SKILL.md frontmatter と trace の両方に固定する。"
    },
    {
      "id": "notion-register",
      "step": 10,
      "title": "Notion スキル一覧 DB へプラグイン情報を upsert (1:1 でヒアリングシート紐付け)",
      "dependsOn": ["trace-write"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "ref", "assign", "delegate", "wrap"],
      "flag_required": "--notion-register",
      "resourceIds": [],
      "output_artifact": "scripts/notion-upsert-plugin.py --plugin <plugin> [--hearing-sheet-id <id>]",
      "note": "実体は top-level scripts/notion-upsert-plugin.py。冪等。token は .notion-config.json の keychain_service/keychain_account から取得し、CI では INTAKE_ALLOW_ENV_TOKEN=1 明示時のみ $NOTION_TOKEN を許可。"
    },
    {
      "id": "feedback-deploy",
      "step": 11,
      "title": "量産先プラグインに run-skill-feedback を実体コピー配備 (default-ON, deployment action)",
      "dependsOn": ["trace-write"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "ref", "assign", "delegate", "wrap"],
      "default_on": true,
      "opt_out_flag": "--no-feedback-loop",
      "resourceIds": [],
      "output_artifact": "<target-plugin>/skills/run-skill-feedback (self-contained copy)",
      "verifier": "scripts/lint-feedback-protocol.py --strict (R7)",
      "note": "build 完了時に必ず実行。harness-creator 自身は対象外。冪等 (既存実体は再コピーしない、既存 symlink は実体へ置換)。これは SKILL.md patch combinator ではなく、scripts/render-combinators.py apply_feedback_loop() の副作用付き deployment action。"
    },
    {
      "id": "content-review",
      "step": 12,
      "title": "Verification obligation DAG 解決 (machine-first; semantic slicing)",
      "dependsOn": ["trace-write", "feedback-deploy"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "ref", "assign", "delegate", "wrap"],
      "default_on": true,
      "opt_out_flag": "--skip-content-review",
      "resourceIds": ["schema-verification-contract", "schema-verification-evidence", "ref-verification-obligation-protocol", "schema-content-review-verdict", "ref-content-review-protocol"],
      "output_artifact": "eval-log/<plugin>/build/{verification-contract.json,verification-plan.json,obligation-evidence/*.json} + legacy content-review projections",
      "verifier": "scripts/lint-content-review.py --changed-only --base origin/main",
      "execution": "deterministic-resolver-then-local-llm-exception",
      "note": "derive-verification-contract.py でgraph全体をclaim DAG化し、plan-verification-obligations.py がexact proof reuse→deterministic check→未解決semantic batchの順に解決する。LLM起動はllm_batches[]だけ。4条件/rubricは同じsemantic obligationで判定し、legacy 2 verdictへprojectionしてreceiptにも束縛する。30思考法3並列はexhaustive audit obligationのみ。反復findingはautomation_candidatesからlint/schema/testへ昇格する。"
    },
    {
      "id": "live-acceptance",
      "step": 13,
      "title": "実走 acceptance (live-trial, Gate D) — behavioral trait 該当 skill のみ条件発火",
      "dependsOn": ["content-review"],
      "kind_filter": ["run", "assign", "delegate", "wrap"],
      "default_on": false,
      "execution": "local-only",
      "trigger": {
        "acceptance_tier": "live",
        "behavioral_sha_changed": true,
        "budget_within": true
      },
      "unconditional": ["proof"],
      "resourceIds": [],
      "output_artifact": "eval-log/<plugin>/<skill>/live-trial/<run-id>/{verdict.json, transcript.jsonl}",
      "verifier": "scripts/lint-live-trial-verdict.py --plugin <plugin> (D13 record-only WARN。P3 常設化 go/no-go で --enforce へ昇格)",
      "note": "Step12 resolverのobservational_queue[]に入ったobligationだけを実走する。plan-live-trials.py はlive executor adapterとして対象skill内で挙動closure/transcript proofを再確認するが、plugin全skillを独自にfan-outしない。incremental既定のtrial/同時実行上限は暴走安全弁。exhaustive明示時のみ全candidate再実走。非発火はdeferred記録。リモートCIは実走せず証跡を機械検査する。"
    }
  ],
  "resources": [
    {"id": "ref-resource-map", "kind": "reference", "path": "./references/resource-map.yaml", "phaseIds": ["init"]},
    {"id": "ref-build-steps", "kind": "reference", "path": "./references/build-steps.md", "phaseIds": ["init", "references"]},
    {"id": "schema-template-selection", "kind": "schema", "path": "./schemas/template-selection.schema.json", "phaseIds": ["init-pre", "scaffold", "templates"]},
    {"id": "schema-skill-build-trace", "kind": "schema", "path": "./schemas/skill-build-trace.schema.json", "phaseIds": ["scripts", "trace-write"]},
    {"id": "schema-responsibility-slot", "kind": "schema", "path": "./schemas/responsibility-slot.schema.json", "phaseIds": ["prompts-emit"]},
    {"id": "schema-build-flags", "kind": "schema", "path": "./schemas/build-flags.schema.json", "phaseIds": ["init", "evaluator-emit"]},
    {"id": "schema-build-plan", "kind": "schema", "path": "./schemas/build-plan.schema.json", "phaseIds": ["init", "scripts"]},
    {"id": "schema-content-review-verdict", "kind": "schema", "path": "./schemas/content-review-verdict.schema.json", "phaseIds": ["content-review"]},
    {"id": "schema-verification-contract", "kind": "schema", "path": "./schemas/verification-contract.schema.json", "phaseIds": ["content-review"]},
    {"id": "schema-verification-evidence", "kind": "schema", "path": "./schemas/verification-evidence.schema.json", "phaseIds": ["content-review"]},
    {"id": "schema-route-build-report", "kind": "schema", "path": "./schemas/route-build-report.schema.json", "phaseIds": ["trace-write"]},
    {"id": "ref-route-build-report", "kind": "reference", "path": "./references/route-build-report.md", "phaseIds": ["trace-write"]},
    {"id": "ref-content-review-protocol", "kind": "reference", "path": "./references/content-review-protocol.md", "phaseIds": ["content-review"]},
    {"id": "ref-verification-obligation-protocol", "kind": "reference", "path": "./references/verification-obligation-protocol.md", "phaseIds": ["content-review"]},
    {"id": "prompt-scaffold", "kind": "prompt", "path": "./prompts/R1-scaffold.md", "phaseIds": ["scaffold"]},
    {"id": "prompt-template-select", "kind": "prompt", "path": "./prompts/R3-template-select.md", "phaseIds": ["scaffold"]},
    {"id": "prompt-responsibility-emit", "kind": "prompt", "path": "./prompts/R2-responsibility-emit.md", "phaseIds": ["prompts-emit"]},
    {"id": "prompt-trace-write", "kind": "prompt", "path": "./prompts/R4-trace-write.md", "phaseIds": ["trace-write"]}
  ]
}
